Adunni Ade has just revealed her mother is at the hospital and in actually fact, ‘fighting’ to life.The actress shared the photos saying she didn’t want to talk about her health online, but she had to do it, to celebrate a strong woman — her mother.Sharing the photos, the mom actress wrote;”I didn’t wanna post this but I wanna celebrate this Strong Woman. You don’t deserve half of the negativity but you’ve always pulled through and this isn’t different. I wanna celebrate you while you’re still here. I loved you before I met you, I still love you until tomorrow. Not yet mama! My Fighter!”May the Lord HEAL her! Amen!! Source